archimate:DataObject.name: AppliedCustomerBillingProductOneTimeCharge
archimate:DataObject.documentation: AppliedCustomerBillingProductOneTimeCharge represents an amount; usually of money; for which an Individual or Organization is financially liable due to a one-time event relating to a Product. For example; $20 installation fee for a home gateway; $600 purchase price for an iPhone; $10 shipping fee for a router.
